}

var exp_month = parseInt(exp.substring(4,6));

var leftStart = table_body.scrollLeft;
var topStart = table_body.scrollTop;
var isLocked = false;
var isLeft = false;
 
var xStart = 0;
var yStart = 0;
var xNow = 0;
var yNow = 0;

var diffX = 0;
var diffY = 0;

var lockInterval;

table_body.addEventListener("touchmove",function(event){
 var pos = touchPosition(event);
 xNow = pos.x;
 yNow = pos.y;
 event.preventDefault();
 
 if(isLocked) {
 diffX = Math.abs(xNow - xStart);
 diffY = Math.abs(yNow - yStart);
 
 //console.log("is locked and coords are",diffX,diffY);
 //table_body.classList.add("scrollNone");
 
 if(diffX >= diffY) {
 //console.log("scroll left");
 table_body.scrollLeft = leftStart - (xNow - xStart);
 table_head.scrollLeft = table_body.scrollLeft;
 
 } else {
 //console.log("scroll up");
 table_body.scrollTop = topStart - (yNow - yStart);
 }
 }
});
var scrollSelectThreshold = 110; //ms
table_body.addEventListener("touchstart",function(event){
 var pos = touchPosition(event);
 xStart = pos.x;
 yStart = pos.y;
 //event.preventDefault();
 table_body.classList.add("scrollNone");

 leftStart = table_body.scrollLeft;
 topStart = table_body.scrollTop;
 
 //console.log("touch");
 
 setTimeout(function(){
 
 if(!isLocked) {
 
 if(diffX >= diffY) {
 yStart = yNow;
 } else {
 xStart = xNow;
 }
 
 //table_body.classList.add("scrollNone");
 isLocked = true;
 } 
 },scrollSelectThreshold);
});
table_body.addEventListener("touchend",function(event){
 isLocked = false;
 table_body.classList.remove("scrollNone");
});

var touchPosition = function(e) {
 if(e.type == 'touchstart' || e.type == 'touchmove' || 
 e.type == 'touchend' || e.type == 'touchcancel')
 {
 //console.log(e.touches,e.changedTouches);
 var touch = e.touches[0] || e.changedTouches[0];
 x = touch.pageX;
 y = touch.pageY;
 
 } else if (e.type == 'mousedown' || e.type == 'mouseup' || 
 e.type == 'mousemove' || e.type == 'mouseover'|| 
 e.type=='mouseout' || e.type=='mouseenter' || e.type=='mouseleave') 
 {
 x = e.clientX;
 y = e.clientY;
 }
 
 return {
 x : x,
 y : y
 };
};

// Bubble sort Implementation using JavaScript

// Creating the bblSort function
function bblSort(orig) {
 var arr = orig;

 for (var i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
 
 var index_i = parseFloat(arr[i].split("_")[0]);
 
 // Last i elements are already in place 
 for (var j = 0; j < (arr.length - i - 1); j++) {
 
 var index_j = parseFloat(arr[j].split("_")[0]);
 
 if(index_i !== undefined && index_j !== undefined) {
 
 }
 
 var index_j2 = parseFloat(arr[j+1].split("_")[0]);

 // Checking if the item at present iteration 
 // is greater than the next iteration
 if (index_j > index_j2) {

 // If the condition is true
 // then swap them
 var temp = arr[j]
 arr[j] = arr[j + 1]
 arr[j + 1] = temp
 }
 }
 }

 //return ([undefined]).concat(arr);
 return arr;
}

objects = bblSort(objects);
VARS["objects_list"] = objects;

// create annotations
for(var obj=0;obj<objects.length;obj++) {
//for(var obj=0;obj<2;obj++) {

for(var p=0;p<soft_load.length;p++) 
{

 // Set the end of the last category length

 });

 } else if (!Number.isInteger(obj[0])) {

 if(play.getElementsByClassName("fa-play").length > 0) {

 audio.play();
 } else {
 audio.pause();
 }
 }
});
